43 NAN_METHOD(steamPropertiesData) {
44  inp = info[0]->ToObject();
45  r = Nan::New<Object>();
46 
47 
48  if (getBool("wantEntropy")) {
49  std::vector<std::array<double, 3>> results;
50  auto const pressure = getDouble("pressure");
51 
52  for (double entropy = 0; entropy < 10.000001; entropy += 0.1) {
53  auto const sp = SteamProperties(pressure, SteamProperties::ThermodynamicQuantity::ENTROPY,
54  entropy).calculate();
55  if (std::isnan(sp.pressure) || std::isnan(sp.temperature) || std::isnan(sp.specificEntropy)
56  || sp.pressure < 0 || sp.temperature < 0 || sp.specificEntropy < 0) {
57  continue;
58  }
59  results.push_back({{sp.pressure, sp.temperature, sp.specificEntropy}});
60  }
61 
62  Handle <Array> data = Array::New(v8::Isolate::GetCurrent(), results.size());
63  for (std::size_t i = 0; i < results.size(); i++) {
64  auto obj = Nan::New<Object>();
65  setRobject("pressure", results.at(i).at(0), obj);
66  setRobject("temperature", results.at(i).at(1), obj);
67  setRobject("entropy", results.at(i).at(2), obj);
68  data->Set(i, obj);
69  }
70  Nan::Set(r, Nan::New<String>("results").ToLocalChecked(), data);
71  info.GetReturnValue().Set(r);
72  } else {
73  std::vector<std::array<double, 4>> results;
74  double const temperature = getDouble("temperature");
75 
76  auto const iterate = [&results, temperature](double pressureStart, double pressureEnd, double pressureStep) {
77  const double a = 0.000000001;
78  for (auto pressure = pressureStart; pressure <= pressureEnd + a; pressure += pressureStep) {
79  auto const sp = SteamProperties(pressure, SteamProperties::ThermodynamicQuantity::TEMPERATURE,
80  temperature).calculate();
81  if (std::isnan(sp.pressure) || std::isnan(sp.temperature) || std::isnan(sp.specificEnthalpy)
82  || std::isnan(sp.specificVolume) || sp.pressure < 0 || sp.temperature < 0
83  || sp.specificEnthalpy < 0 || sp.specificVolume < 0) {
84  continue;
85  }
86  results.push_back({{sp.pressure, sp.temperature, sp.specificEnthalpy, sp.specificVolume}});
87  }
88  };
89 
90  iterate(0.0005, 0.01, 0.0005);
91  iterate(0.015, 0.1, 0.005);
92  iterate(0.11, 0.5, 0.01);
93  iterate(0.55, 1, 0.05);
94  iterate(1.1, 5, 0.1);
95  iterate(5.5, 10, 0.5);
96  iterate(11, 25, 1);
97  iterate(30, 100, 5);
98 
99  Handle <Array> data = Array::New(v8::Isolate::GetCurrent(), results.size());
100  for (std::size_t i = 0; i < results.size(); i++) {
101  auto obj = Nan::New<Object>();
102  setRobject("pressure", results.at(i).at(0), obj);
103  setRobject("temperature", results.at(i).at(1), obj);
104  setRobject("enthalpy", results.at(i).at(2), obj);
105  setRobject("volume", results.at(i).at(3), obj);
106  data->Set(i, obj);
107  }
108  Nan::Set(r, Nan::New<String>("results").ToLocalChecked(), data);
109  info.GetReturnValue().Set(r);
110  }
111 }

460 NAN_METHOD(header) {
461  inp = info[0]->ToObject();
462  r = Nan::New<Object>();
463 
464  auto const headerPressure = getDouble("headerPressure");
465 
466  Local <String> arrayStr = Nan::New<String>("inlets").ToLocalChecked();
467  auto array = inp->ToObject()->Get(arrayStr);
468  v8::Local <v8::Array> arr = v8::Local<v8::Array>::Cast(array);
469 
470  auto pressureStr = Nan::New<String>("pressure").ToLocalChecked();
471  auto temperatureStr = Nan::New<String>("temperature").ToLocalChecked();
472  auto qualityStr = Nan::New<String>("quality").ToLocalChecked();
473  auto massFlowStr = Nan::New<String>("massFlow").ToLocalChecked();
474  auto specificEnthalpyStr = Nan::New<String>("specificEnthalpy").ToLocalChecked();
475  auto specificEntropyStr = Nan::New<String>("specificEntropy").ToLocalChecked();
476  auto energyFlowStr = Nan::New<String>("energyFlow").ToLocalChecked();
477 
478  std::vector<Inlet> inlets;
479 
480  for (std::size_t i = 0; i < arr->Length(); i++) {
481  auto const pressure = arr->Get(i)->ToObject()->Get(pressureStr)->NumberValue();
482  unsigned val = static_cast<unsigned>(arr->Get(i)->ToObject()->Get(
483  Nan::New<String>("thermodynamicQuantity").ToLocalChecked())->NumberValue());
484  auto const quantity = static_cast<SteamProperties::ThermodynamicQuantity>(val);
485  auto const quantityValue = arr->Get(i)->ToObject()->Get(
486  Nan::New<String>("quantityValue").ToLocalChecked())->NumberValue();
487  auto const massFlow = arr->Get(i)->ToObject()->Get(massFlowStr)->NumberValue();
488  inlets.emplace_back(Inlet(pressure, quantity, quantityValue, massFlow));
489 
490  Local <Object> obj = Nan::New<Object>();
491  Local <String> inletNum = Nan::New<String>("inlet" + std::to_string(i + 1)).ToLocalChecked();
492  auto const inletProps = inlets[i].getInletProperties();
493 
494  Nan::Set(obj, pressureStr, Nan::New<Number>(inletProps.pressure));
495  Nan::Set(obj, temperatureStr, Nan::New<Number>(inletProps.temperature));
496  Nan::Set(obj, qualityStr, Nan::New<Number>(inletProps.quality));
497  Nan::Set(obj, specificEnthalpyStr, Nan::New<Number>(inletProps.specificEnthalpy));
498  Nan::Set(obj, specificEntropyStr, Nan::New<Number>(inletProps.specificEntropy));
499  Nan::Set(obj, energyFlowStr, Nan::New<Number>(inlets[i].getInletEnergyFlow()));
500  Nan::Set(obj, massFlowStr, Nan::New<Number>(inlets[i].getMassFlow()));
501 
502  Nan::Set(r, inletNum, obj);
503  }
504 
505  try {
506  auto header = Header(headerPressure, inlets);
507  Local <String> headerStr = Nan::New<String>("header").ToLocalChecked();
508 
509  auto const headerProps = header.getHeaderProperties();
510 
511  Local <Object> obj = Nan::New<Object>();
512 
513  Nan::Set(obj, pressureStr, Nan::New<Number>(header.getHeaderPressure()));
514  Nan::Set(obj, temperatureStr, Nan::New<Number>(headerProps.temperature));
515  Nan::Set(obj, qualityStr, Nan::New<Number>(headerProps.quality));
516  Nan::Set(obj, specificEnthalpyStr, Nan::New<Number>(headerProps.specificEnthalpy));
517  Nan::Set(obj, specificEntropyStr, Nan::New<Number>(headerProps.specificEntropy));
518  Nan::Set(obj, energyFlowStr, Nan::New<Number>(header.getInletEnergyFlow()));
519  Nan::Set(obj, massFlowStr, Nan::New<Number>(header.getInletMassFlow()));
520 
521  Nan::Set(r, headerStr, obj);
522  } catch (std::runtime_error const &e) {
523  std::string const what = e.what();
524  ThrowError(std::string("std::runtime_error thrown in header - ssmt.h: " + what).c_str());
525  }
526  info.GetReturnValue().Set(r);
527 }

529 NAN_METHOD(turbine) {
530  inp = info[0]->ToObject();
531  r = Nan::New<Object>();
